Package com.flipfit.bean

Class Slot

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.Slot
public class Slot extends Object
Represents a bookable time slot at a gym. This class stores information about a specific time period, including its capacity and assigned trainer, and tracks the number of booked seats.
Author:
Prisha

      public Slot(String slotId, String startTime, String endTime, int numOfSeats, String trainer, String gymId)
      Constructs a new Slot with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      slotId - The unique identifier for the slot.
      startTime - The start time of the slot (e.g., "09:00 AM").
      endTime - The end time of the slot (e.g., "10:00 AM").
      numOfSeats - The total number of available seats in the slot.
      trainer - The name of the trainer assigned to this slot.
      gymId - The unique identifier of the gym this slot belongs to.
